name: SoLex
description:
This is a lot of 2 crossbody bags.
 Included are: 
 ~ A black bag that features a faux leather textured material, an adjustable shoulder strap, and a snap closure for the main bag. Inside the main bag is a zip-up pocket on one side. It measures about 9 tall without the strap, 23.25 tall with the strap, 7.5 wide, 5.5 deep. There was a bag inside the bag but it was cut off. 
 ~ A black bag that features a faux leather textured material, an adjustable shoulder strap, a snap front pocket, and a zip-up closure for the main bag. Inside the main bag is a zip-up pocket on one side and two open pockets on the other side. It measures about 8.5 tall without the strap, 31 tall with the strap, 8 wide, and 1.5 deep.
 These items come in good pre-owned condition with stains.
